28 May 2008Government has noted with concern media reports that Cabinet has taken a decision to establish refugee camps. Government wish to put it on the record that Cabinet has not taken such a decision and that the reports are baseless and therefore not true.An announcement on the government s position will be made at the Post-Cabinet media briefing tomorrow.Enquiries Themba Maseko Cell: 083 645 0810Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)